Ambrosia Apple Slices with Peanut Butter

5 min
$3.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Peanuts

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeNut-Free Option Available

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Snack

Tags:

SnackHealthyQuickEasy

Description

A refreshing and protein-packed snack that combines sweet Ambrosia apple slices with creamy peanut butter for a delightful crunch.

Ingredients

  • ambrosia apples: 2
  • peanut butter: 4 tablespoons
  • honey: 1 tablespoon
  • cinnamon: 1 teaspoon
